No. 10-1489. Mai-Trang Thi Nguyen, Petitioner v. Starbucks Coffee Corporation. 565 U.S. 930, 132 S. Ct. 368,

181 L. Ed. 2d 234,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6786, October 3, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Justice Breyer took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 418 Fed. Appx. 606.
